header.gameNote: NEW YORK LIFE ACC MEN'S TOURNAMENT - QUARTERFINAL

videos.description: Quentin Snider finds Anas Mahmoud alone under the basket and tosses him an alley-oop as the Cardinals jump out to an early lead.
videos.headline: Louisville takes early lead on Mahmoud oop

videos.description: Virginia's Ty Jerome drives the lane and gets the hoop and harm on an awkward one-handed finish.
videos.headline: Jerome shows strength on and-1

videos.description: Devon Hall misses the transition triple, but Mamadi Diakite hustles for the rebound and putback.
videos.headline: Diakite storms lane for putback slam

videos.description: Virginia's Kyle Guy unleashes a long 3-pointer to put the No. 1 Cavaliers back up 10 in the second half.
videos.headline: Guy extends lead on Louisville with deep 3

videos.description: Jordan Nwora gets the ball in transition and beats Mamadi Diakite to the rim as Louisville trails No. 1 Virginia 56-52.
videos.headline: Louisville bench loves Nwora slam

videos.description: Devon Hall gets the ball in the corner and makes a quick move to the basket for a layup.
videos.headline: Hall drives baseline for layup
